scripts.deploy:dev: npm run server:kill && npm run migrate && npm run server:restart:deployment
scripts.deploy:staging: npm run lint:check && npm run test && npm run migrate && npm run server:restart:deployment
scripts.deploy:prod: npm run lint:check && npm run test && npm run migrate && npm run theme:protect && npm run server:restart:deployment
scripts.migrate:fresh: npm run server:kill && node scripts/database-migrator.js fresh && npm run server:restart:migration
scripts.language:sync: npm run server:kill && node scripts/language-manager.js sync && npm run server:restart:language
scripts.ci:prepare: npm install && npm run lint:check && npm run test
scripts.ci:deploy: npm run ci:prepare && npm run deploy:prod
scripts.emergency:restore: npm run migrate:rollback && npm run server:restart "Emergency restore" "Emergency"

recommendations.message: Consider adding React.memo, useCallback, and useMemo for performance optimization.
